::Kluster::

Kluster nods. "I'll set him on enemy," he says, tapping a few keys and doing 
so.

Kluster turns back to Valtron. "Grimmler is near the entrance of the ship," 
he says, "Find him and tell him I said to come with you. I have to stay at 
the ship."
